snippet.title: Company of Heroes 3 | Console Gameplay Reveal
snippet.description:
Description Company of Heroes 3 has been meticulously redesigned for Console, with intuitive controller support, custom console UI, and features that allow you to play at your own pace. 

Find out more on our website! https://www.companyofheroes.com/en/company-of-heroes-3-console-edition

Follow Company of Heroes on socials:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CompanyOfHeroes
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/companyofheroes/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/companyofheroes/
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/relicentertainment

#CompanyofHeroes #CoH3
